NK015(ba)009:0: dpal gsang ba snying po'i brgyud 'debs ku mud phreng ba'i don bsdus bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)009:1: e wam rang bzhin rdo rje dril bu 'chang //
NK015(ba)009:2: sgyu ma'i rang bzhin rol pa'i gar gyis sgeg /
NK015(ba)009:3: bde stong rang bzhin kha sbyor bdun gyis bdag /
NK015(ba)009:4: lhan skyes rang bzhin rdo rje sems dpa' rgyal //
NK015(ba)009:5: gsang ba'i bdag po rigs can d+r+wa ma lnga //
NK015(ba)009:6: lung bstan rdo rje ku ku r+aa dza'i zhabs //
NK015(ba)009:7: sh+aakya pu tri sa brgyad sems ma la //
NK015(ba)009:8: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin brlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK015(ba)009:9: rdo rje yon tan gzungs dang h'u ka ra //
NK015(ba)009:10: pra b+ha ha sti sangs rgyas gsang ba'i zhabs //
NK015(ba)009:11: slob dpon pad+ma pan chen bi ma lar //
NK015(ba)009:12: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin brlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK015(ba)009:13: rin chen mchog dang kye re mchog skyong dang //
NK015(ba)009:14: rgyal ba'i yon tan gnubs chen rin po che //
NK015(ba)009:15: yon tan rgya mtsho ye shes rgya mtsho la //
NK015(ba)009:16: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin brlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK015(ba)009:17: blo gros byang chub bde gshegs zur po che //
NK015(ba)009:18: shes rab grags pa yang khyed sgro phug pa //
NK015(ba)009:19: rdzogs chen par grags bla ma rin po che //
NK015(ba)009:20: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin rlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK015(ba)009:21: sku gsum mngon du gyur pa'i kahthoga pa //
NK015(ba)009:22: de sras sa bcu'i dbang phyug gtsang ston zhabs //
NK015(ba)009:23: thugs rje mtshungs med byams pa 'bum pa la //
NK015(ba)009:24: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin brlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK015(ba)009:25: nam mkha' rdo rje thugs rje ye shes dang //
NK015(ba)009:26: ston pa dbang 'byor rje btsun dpal 'bar ba //
NK015(ba)009:27: mgon po rgyal mtshan tshul khrims rgyal mtshan la //
NK015(ba)009:28: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin brlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK015(ba)009:29: d+harma klak+sha ye shes rgyal mtshan rje //
NK015(ba)009:30: nam mkha' rgyal mtshan mtshungs med nam mkha' dpal //
NK015(ba)009:31: nam mkha' rgya mtsho chos kyi dbang po la //
NK015(ba)009:32: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin brlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK015(ba)009:33: bsod nams rdo rje he ba chos 'byung dang //
NK015(ba)009:34: sh+aakya bkra shis rin chen rdo rje'i zhabs //
NK015(ba)009:35: sangs rgyas bkra shis sh+aakya tshe ring la //
NK015(ba)009:36: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin brlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK015(ba)009:37: o rgyan phun tshogs thugs kyi rdo rje dang //
NK015(ba)009:38: blo gros chen po kun mkhyen si tu pa //
NK015(ba)009:39: chos kyi rgya mtsho 'khor lo'i dbang phyug la //
NK015(ba)009:40: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin brlabs dngos grub stsol /
NK015(ba)009:42: / 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang du //
NK015(ba)009:43: dam pa'i mdzod 'chang kun bzang dgongs pa'i rtsal //
NK015(ba)009:44: mngon rdzogs dus gsum sgyu 'phrul bla ma la //
NK015(ba)009:45: gsol 'debs phyag 'tshal byin brlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK015(ba)009:46: yid kyi lha sku stobs rdzogs rnam par smin //
NK015(ba)009:47: lus sems rdo rje'i gnas grub tshe la dabnga /
NK015(ba)009:49: / 'ja' lus g.yo ba med pa phyag rgya che //
NK015(ba)009:50: rtsol med lhun grub rig 'dzin bzhi bsgrod shog /
